### Create a NPC
# @name create
POST http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/create
content-type: application/json

{
  "type": "goblin",
  "locationId": "b80c8112-f389-49a7-8cf6-4aad3b3ec601"
}

### Get new NPC id
@agentId = {{create.response.body.$.entities[0].id}}

### Get NPC  
GET http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}

### Describe NPC 
GET http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}/describe

### Get ALL NPCs
GET http://localhost:4000/api/npcs

### Damage an NPC
POST http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}/damage
content-type: application/json

{
  "value": {{$randomInt 2 8}}
}

### Move a NPC somewhere
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}/move/c09e4f2b-91cd-4d0e-a173-6ff23e68d6e1
